name: Celebrity Wheel of Fortune
overview: Hosted by Pat Sajak and Vanna White, celebrity contestants spin the wheel and solve word puzzles for a chance to win up to one million dollars for charity.
tagline: The world's most famous wheel has gone Hollywood
